B.  Soft tissue, small bowel implant #2, biopsy:  Granulation tissue with marked acute and chronic inflammation. Negative for malignancy.

C.  Soft tissue, necrotic tumor, biopsy:  Moderately differentiated adenocarcinoma.

D.  Ileum, terminal and partial ascending colon, resection:  Multi-focal serosal serosal involvement by moderately differentiated adenocarcinoma.  

